{"id":2622,"date":"2025-05-13T15:57:30","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T08:57:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2622"},"modified":"2025-05-15T14:38:36","modified_gmt":"2025-05-15T07:38:36","slug":"chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-hieu-qua","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-hieu-qua\/","title":{"rendered":"5 C\u00e1ch ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 &#8211; B\u00ed quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>\u201cCh\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t\u201d<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb9p quan t\u00e2m, b\u1edfi l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i v\u1ebb r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin. Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra do c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 n\u1ed9i sinh (suy gi\u1ea3m collagen, n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1) v\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i sinh (tia UV, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m, l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng). Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, GSC s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da v\u00e0 c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt b\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t 2025 t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ly-do-khien-da-lao-hoa-som-chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-don-gian-khong\"><\/span><b>L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 s\u1edbm? Ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 do nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c nhau, c\u1ea3 t\u1eeb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i l\u1eabn b\u00ean trong c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 da m\u1eb7t, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2628\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2628\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2628 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat.webp\" alt=\"L\u00fd do da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2628\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>L\u00fd do da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"yeu-to-tu-ben-trong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c: M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 l\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, c\u0169ng s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac da v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 oxy t\u1edbi da b\u1ecb gi\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n, l\u00e0n da s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 di truy\u1ec1n: Di truy\u1ec1n, bao g\u1ed3m s\u1eafc t\u1ed9c v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i da, l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 b\u1ea9m sinh m\u00e0 m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi mang theo. Ch\u00ednh di truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"yeu-to-tu-ben-ngoai\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u201coxy ho\u00e1 da\u201d. <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ed7i n\u0103m, da ti\u1ebfp t\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ed7i nhi\u1ec1u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f4 li\u00ean k\u1ebft, s\u1ee3i collagen v\u00e0 s\u1ee3i elastin trong da. N\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, che ch\u1eafn th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ecb n\u00e1m s\u1ebd cao h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng k\u1ef9.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh oxy ho\u00e1 tr\u00ean da, khi\u1ebfn da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 thi\u1ebfu ng\u1ee7, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n d\u1ea7u m\u1ee1, u\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ecdt hay s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch c\u0169ng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0m da l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 s\u1edbm.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dau-hieu-nhan-biet-lao-hoa-da-chuan-2025\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da chu\u1ea9n 2025<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00e3o h\u00f3a da l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m da m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, n\u00e1m, v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 cho th\u1ea5y l\u00e0n da \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u00e3o h\u00f3a:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2624\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2624\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2624 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-gsc.webp\" alt=\"D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da chu\u1ea9n 2025\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-gsc.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-gsc-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-gsc-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-gsc-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2624\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da chu\u1ea9n 2025<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7n s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c ng\u1ee9a, d\u1ec5 bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to h\u01a1n do s\u1ef1 suy gi\u1ea3m collagen.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Qu\u1ea7ng th\u00e2m v\u00e0 b\u1ecdng m\u1eaft tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y khi da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t, ng\u1ef1c, v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1m \u0111\u1ed3i m\u1ed3i, n\u00e1m ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0n da s\u1ea1m m\u00e0u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfp nh\u0103n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n, da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1ea3y x\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc v\u1ed1n c\u00f3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1ecfng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng do y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u1ea1ch m\u00e1u d\u01b0\u1edbi da k\u00e9m \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb b\u1ea7m t\u00edm h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da m\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng sau khi b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng ho\u1eb7c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-tuong-nao-tang-nguy-co-lao-hoa-da-som\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da s\u1edbm?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00e3o h\u00f3a da l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nh\u00f3m ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y nhanh h\u01a1n:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2625\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2625\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2625 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-2025.webp\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da s\u1edbm\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-2025.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-2025-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-2025-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-2025-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2625\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>\u0110\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0o t\u0103ng nguy c\u01a1 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da s\u1edbm<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tia UV nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 m\u00e1y nhu\u1ed9m da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ed1ng trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3i b\u1ee5i v\u00e0 h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Di truy\u1ec1n c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 vitamin C, E v\u00e0 collagen.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1ed1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng c\u00f3 kh\u00ed h\u1eadu nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c c\u1eadn nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t k\u00edch th\u00edch nh\u01b0 r\u01b0\u1ee3u bia, c\u00e0 ph\u00ea khi\u1ebfn da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 l\u00e0m suy gi\u1ea3m collagen.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-ngan-ngua-lao-hoa-hieu-qua-cho-tung-do-tuoi\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2627\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2627\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2627 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2627\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cham-soc-da-tuoi-25\"><\/span><b>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da tu\u1ed5i 25<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 20-25, l\u00e0n da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3m s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t collagen, khi\u1ebfn da m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a nh\u1eb9. \u0110\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec v\u1ebb tr\u1ebb trung, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng: Ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, gi\u00fap da lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Duy tr\u00ec th\u00f3i quen thoa kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng SPF 30+ h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u1ed3i trong nh\u00e0 hay ra ngo\u00e0i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t: B\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a ch\u1ee9a retinoids, vitamin C gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00f9ng da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m: D\u00f9ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng cho v\u00f9ng da m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">U\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u01b0\u1edbc, duy tr\u00ec gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc gi\u00fap da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bi-quyet-chong-lao-hoa-cho-do-tuoi-tu-30\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 cho \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 30<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30, l\u00e0n da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a nh\u01b0 n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, n\u00e1m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1eef g\u00ecn l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2626\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2626\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2626 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-tai-nha.webp\" alt=\"B\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 cho \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 30\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-tai-nha.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-tai-nha-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-tai-nha-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-tai-nha-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2626\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>B\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 cho \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 30<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, tr\u00e1nh c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a sulfate v\u00ec ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc (AHA, BHA): Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ednh \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed5 sung serum vitamin C: Gi\u00fap da s\u00e1ng, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Duy tr\u00ec kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n LED.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed5 sung collagen v\u00e0 hyaluronic acid: Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-o-do-tuoi-40\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00e1ch ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 40<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tu\u1ed5i 40, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da di\u1ec5n ra nhanh h\u01a1n do s\u1ef1 suy gi\u1ea3m collagen v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i hormone. Da b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia UV.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Duy tr\u00ec quy tr\u00ecnh skincare ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: T\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o h\u00f3a chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da v\u1edbi m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1, serum ch\u1ee9a retinoids\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ed5 sung collagen v\u00e0 vitamin C: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chong-lao-hoa-da-%e2%80%93-voi-da-kho-nam-sam\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da &#8211; V\u1edbi da kh\u00f4 n\u00e1m s\u1ea1m<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u: D\u00f9ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 tinh ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb n\u00e1m, s\u1ea1m da: C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem b\u00f4i, thu\u1ed1c u\u1ed1ng, laser ho\u1eb7c peel da \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 da trong ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"doi-voi-da-nhan-co-nhu-cau-tre-hoa-chay-xe\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi da nh\u0103n, c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u tr\u1ebb ho\u00e1, ch\u1ea3y x\u1ec7<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u00eam axit hyaluronic: L\u00e0m \u0111\u1ea7y r\u00e3nh nh\u0103n, gi\u00fap da c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ti\u00eam botox: Gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00e1n, kh\u00f3e m\u1eaft.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Laser t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da: Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m m\u1edd c\u00e1c n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n m\u00e0u s\u1eafc da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9: Th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u0103ng da v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phuong-phap-chong-lao-hoa-da-mat-hieu-qua-tai-nha\"><\/span><b>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p\u00a0ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2597\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2597\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2597 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc.webp\" alt=\"GSC M\u1eb7t N\u1ea1 N\u00e2ng C\u01a1\" width=\"1200\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/mat-na-gel-gsc-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2597\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>GSC M\u1eb7t N\u1ea1 N\u00e2ng C\u01a1<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da &#8211; L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ea9y trang + r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t. \u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang( cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m) v\u00e0 s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t pH 5.5.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sau b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch, th\u00ec b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1ee1ng cho da v\u1edbi serum d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m\/kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m c\u0169ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u1edbi l\u00e0n da \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u SPF 30+ m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 \u1edf trong hay ngo\u00e0i nh\u00e0 nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ri\u00eang v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da n\u00e1m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m gi\u00fap k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m n\u00e1m. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n m\u00e0 ch\u1ecb em c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean gia GSC t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n: Retinol\/vitamin C.\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, ch\u1ecb em c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00eam m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 n\u00e2ng c\u01a1 gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da nh\u1eb9.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">GSC mong r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. \u0110\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb, h\u00e3y ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, tia UV v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng. M\u1ed9t chu tr\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi th\u00f3i quen s\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n <\/span><b>ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, gi\u1eef m\u00e3i n\u00e9t r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 theo th\u1eddi gian!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u201cCh\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da m\u1eb7t\u201d l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1i \u0111\u1eb9p quan t\u00e2m, b\u1edfi l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i v\u1ebb r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2627,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[12],"class_list":["post-2622","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh","tag-lam-dep-da"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2622","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2622"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2622\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3032,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2622\/revisions\/3032"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2627"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-js